/**
 * Admin Guidance Defaults API
 *
 * GET  /api/admin/guidance-center/defaults/:type - Get default guidance profile
 * PUT  /api/admin/guidance-center/defaults/:type - Update default guidance profile
 *
 * Note: Authentication is handled by middleware in src/index.ts, not here.
